{"_id":"GTUSNOLiCJJxCvZt","name":"Chimera","type":"Monster","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/monsters/griffin-symbol.svg","data":{"resources":{"actionsPerRound":{"value":1,"max":2},"stamina":{"value":42,"max":42}},"biography":{"notes":"Poisonous","description":"<p>A bizarre combination of creatures, the chimera has the body of a lion, the tail of a scorpion and the heads of a dragon, a lion and a goat. It is a magical creature, created by ancient warlocks as a beast of war. Its nature is aggressive as it is full of pain, its body rebelling against the sorceries that hold it together. The scorpion tail and claws of the chimera drip an acidic venom, making areas it passes through smoke and reek.</p>"},"gear":{"weapons":[],"armour":[],"equipment":[]},"type":"Monster","weaponSkill":7,"adventuringSkills":5},"token":{"name":"Chimera","img":"systems/warlock/assets/icons/griffin-symbol.svg","displayName":0,"actorLink":false,"width":1,"height":1,"scale":1,"mirrorX":false,"mirrorY":false,"lockRotation":false,"rotation":0,"alpha":1,"vision":false,"dimSight":0,"brightSight":0,"sightAngle":0,"light":{"alpha":0.5,"angle":0,"bright":0,"coloration":1,"dim":0,"gradual":true,"luminosity":0.5,"saturation":0,"contrast":0,"shadows":0,"animation":{"speed":5,"intensity":5,"reverse":false},"darkness":{"min":0,"max":1}},"disposition":-1,"displayBars":0,"bar1":{"attribute":null},"bar2":{"attribute":null},"flags":{},"randomImg":false},"items":[{"_id":"9z5gI3dLJ4Nn4MbQ","name":"Claw","type":"Weapon","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"","activeSystem":"warlock","isEquipped":true,"type":{"value":"","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Casual":"Casual","Martial":"Martial"},"warpstar":{"":"","Small":"Small","Medium":"Medium","Heavy":"Heavy"}}},"damage":{"roll":"2d6+2","type":{"value":"Slashing","choices":{"warlock":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashing","Blast":"Blast"},"warpstar":{"":"","Crushing":"Crushing","Piercing":"Piercing","Slashing":"Slashin